Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • Entities.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a user that has registered with the MoblimaApp. A user can be either an Admin type or Customer type.
    Since:
    2017-11-16
